Detailed Description

cvmx_hna_sbd_dbg0

When the HNA_CONTROL[SBDLCK] bit is written to 1, the contents of this register are locked down. Otherwise, the contents of this register are the active contents of the HNA scoreboard at the time of the CSR read.
